{"tid":583610,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實軒仔首我的天都幾屈機","createTime":"2018-03-07T06:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T05:45:48.000Z","uid":56567,"like":142,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"90b14a2ca1d615b57e7d4aeefd88e082f87c909f","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"先講講歌詞 節錄:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 多意外　在日落大道的你與我握手<br />\n輕輕說　你發覺太想闖遍這地球<br />\n而一起　空間感恐怕沒有<br />\n想孤身去走</span><br />\n<br />\n不意外是站著造夢的你愛我不久<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 今天說　你對我興趣減退擁夠抱夠</span><br />\n房間中　常常如沉悶困獸<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 門匙遞向我　懶回首</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 為何戀愛可以當做吸過半支煙<br />\n隨時不太高興將那煙蒂放一邊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 為何分手可以當做將細軟搬遷<br />\n臨行給我一句失去感覺我的天<br />\n從聚到散　不講路線<br />\n突然再見　別再見</span><br />\n<br />\n首歌講述一對愛侶，本來平平淡淡咁相處。<br />\n直至有一日，有一方突然提出分手，<br />\n好聽啲就話自己想一個人去闖下世界，<br />\n但其實真實嘅原因好簡單，冇Feel。<br />\n一句嘅冇Feel抹殺嘥兩人嘅付出，回憶。<br />\n面對對方嘅殘酷無情，突然提出嘅分手，<br />\n心裏除咗失樂，仲充滿住無奈。<br />\n「點解吖？明明我哋琴日仲好地地嫁」<br />\n「點解吖？明明我哋仲講好去邊到邊到旅行嫁」<br />\n你不停地追問佢，但佢只繼續放低手上嘅鎖匙<br />\n頭也不回咁一步一步離你而去。<br />\n你決心孭起背囊，繼續從後追返佢<br />\n但可惜無論你點追點挽留<br />\n對方都喺冷酷無情咁拒絕你。<br />\n<br />\n拍拖拍到大家心灰意冷而分手並唔傷感，<br />\n最傷最痛嘅喺突然而來嘅分手。<br />\n<br />\n#我的天#張敬軒#一歌一故事<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-cDq9maci4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-cDq9maci4w&d=IYlurP2LEVsDKdiYVEe4oxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6bf86456\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-cDq9maci4w</a>"},{"pid":"99909be7b3abe7c261d8193d572a02bd6b9cef24","tid":583610,"uid":40194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"而歐洲的星空仍舊很閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d42df6ab9d8c3fed014d2c5542c88a3732f7c55","tid":583610,"uid":62061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:56:06.000Z","msg":"但無情像你般      未見"},{"pid":"f8c888f76ec55f3f391684588dd0b6f3628f573e","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99909be7b3abe7c261d8193d572a02bd6b9cef24","tid":583610,"uid":40194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"而歐洲的星空仍舊很閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"夕爺理兩段呼應得好好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多意外 在日落大道的你與我握手<br />\n輕輕說 你發覺太想闖遍這地球</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">身處在 異地在認路的我太過膚淺</span><br />\n不知道 計算到再准方向都會有變<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而歐洲的星空仍舊很閃<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n好似對方話要走,你自己就繼續追<br />\n你冇諗到追唔追到,<br />\n但就算追得返<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「餘情又哪怕 再遇險」</span>"},{"pid":"7c987fd90b76fa3604179d99ae0e0299eb3db929","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d42df6ab9d8c3fed014d2c5542c88a3732f7c55","tid":583610,"uid":62061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T06:56:06.000Z","msg":"但無情像你般      未見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"一切都太突然,完全冇諗過笑得咁傻咁天真嘅對方,原來喺可以咁冷酷無情"},{"pid":"4e6b8ecd138e0a375206c10fc387f1d72495da6d","tid":583610,"uid":101110,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"分手永遠都係突如其來，因為兩個人一齊係要共識，分手唔需要。或者你會幻想一千幾百次分手情節，即使係噉你永遠都控制唔到對方有咩行動，所以分手永遠都係有突如其來嘅意外。"},{"pid":"3707b4475557bc4941526ada84ed482fef6c46bd","tid":583610,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4cc38cda317a46e9addc652d55ac5c2ee73a26","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6b8ecd138e0a375206c10fc387f1d72495da6d","tid":583610,"uid":101110,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"分手永遠都係突如其來，因為兩個人一齊係要共識，分手唔需要。或者你會幻想一千幾百次分手情節，即使係噉你永遠都控制唔到對方有咩行動，所以分手永遠都係有突如其來嘅意外。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:14:39.000Z","msg":"只要等到一個缺口，就會衝口而出"},{"pid":"6ad202bd8a91ab846d98f4df1a26d531d1440ec2","tid":583610,"uid":151738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2961a0dc18a5a1a7e37b40deaf44129dd043dc","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f81efeea2063d0c52bc97a65eb622cfd4b2b94f","tid":583610,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"我明啊<br />\n我都係咁比人飛<br />\n豪無先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e8e20aba77d04a241a5145d13e6a28f275cc97","tid":583610,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5328538ef5b8842d53b7a720fd94c40add573f","tid":583610,"uid":56567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f81efeea2063d0c52bc97a65eb622cfd4b2b94f","tid":583610,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"我明啊<br />\n我都係咁比人飛<br />\n豪無先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"無先兆嘅分手最難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf90b91943b596c599519cd5e1b58b4b656fd87","tid":583610,"uid":62061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"要變可以好快<br />\n早一晚仲可以係攬住一齊瞓"},{"